<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然是農曆新年，<delay20 />
但也可能和平日相差無幾呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，我非常高興可以過著<delay8 />
有<tag a="110" b="4" />和島上的大家<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />陪伴的日常生活，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是因為農曆新年嗎<tag a="110" b="0" />？<delay20 />
我忍不住想起了老家的事。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等一下去寫張心意卡
寄回老家好了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果依照舊時的曆法來看，<delay20 />
今天是一年的開始呢～<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />今年的目標<delay20 />
再增加一個好了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00">聽說今天是新月，看不見月亮喔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算看不見月亮<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要一想到接下來月亮會慢慢變圓，<delay8 />
就覺得很棒呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過農曆新年<delay20 />
應該怎麼度過<delay8 />才對呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總之先享受美食，<delay20 />
與重要的人一同度過，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />應該就可以了吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
